OL,3,CWoman jailed after trafficking drugs
OL,4,Cdisguised as bath salts through airport
OL,6,FA woman has been jailed for her role
OL,7,Fin trafficking drugs disguised as bath
OL,8,Fsalts through an airport.
OL,10,FAbigail Kavanagh, 25, of Ely, Cardiff,
OL,11,Fwas sentenced at Newport Crown Court
OL,12,Fon October 22 for her role in
OL,13,Ftrafficking the drugs on behalf of an
OL,14,Forganised crime group.
OL,16,FShe was arrested during an operation
OL,17,Frun by Tarian, the Regional Organised
OL,18,FCrime Unit for southern Wales.
