OL,3,CWoman jailed after trafficking drugs
OL,4,Cdisguised as bath salts through airport
OL,6,FOn 8 March, 2024, Border Force
OL,7,Fofficers at East Midlands Airport
OL,8,Fintercepted a package sent from
OL,9,FAustria and destined for Kavanagh's
OL,10,Fhome address.
OL,12,FThe package contained 10 kilograms of
OL,13,FMDMA, disguised as bath salts. The
OL,14,Fdrugs had a potential street value of
OL,15,F#300,000.
OL,17,FKavanagh was arrested at her home
OL,18,Faddress. A review of her mobile phone
OL,19,Ffurther uncovered her involvement in
OL,20,Fthe supply of a Class B drug, Spice,
OL,21,Finto prisons across South Wales.
