OL,6,FHe added that she had also been tasked
OL,7,Fwith arranging deliveries of Spice to
OL,8,Fprisons and collecting cash for the
OL,9,Fgroup.
OL,11,F"Offenders who import and traffic
OL,12,Fdrugs around our communities and
OL,13,Fprisons do not care about the harm
OL,14,Fthey bring. Their sole concern is
OL,15,Fprofit," he continued.
