OL,6,F"Kavanagh has received a lengthy
OL,7,Fcustodial sentence, which sends a
OL,8,Fclear message to those who choose to
OL,9,Fget involved in this type of
OL,10,Fcriminality. Tarian will continue to
OL,11,Fwork closely with partner agencies,
OL,12,Fincluding Border Force and the
OL,13,FNational Crime Agency, to use every
OL,14,Fresource within our power to bring
OL,15,Fthese offenders to justice."
